# AI Transparency Statement

All blog posts are written by me and based on my own thinking. I used to use LLMs for editing (only for fixing grammar or to improve writing style), but after seeing the amount of llm-generated content and how boring it is to read, I've come around to not use it at all.

I do, however, use it as if it were a talking duck (arguably an improvement over the [usual one](https://cdn.lautaroacosta.com/ferris.avif)), to bounce ideas.
